==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Superfetate
<hw>Su`per*fe"tate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>superfetare</ets>; <ets>super</ets> above, over + <ets>fetare</ets>
to bring forth.]</ety> <def>To conceive after a prior conception, but
before the birth of the offspring.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The female . . . is said to <qex>superfetate</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Grew.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Superfetation</ent>⟦br⟧
